    "Hence, we decided to create our own dataset, label (and rephrase) it manually, and use it for in-context learning, finetuning and evaluation.",
    "We collected a set of 1500 queries by using 3 different strategies.",
    "• A set of 600 queries were created semiautomatically.",
    "Multiple associates in our organization recorded an initial set of queries based on their work requirements.",
    "Then Chat-GPT was used as an assistant to generate similar additional queries by using these human authored queries as seeds."
